 results of our X-ray\nanalysis show that current expectations from a ballistic nature of the jets can\nexplain satisfactorily some of the observational evidences but cannot fully\nreproduce the observations. The alternative scenario (diffusion of particles\nalong preexisting magnetic field lines in the surrounding medium) however also\ncontinues to suffer from conflicts with the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2015 22:52:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
