n the intervals are\nsymmetric, i.e. $-a_1=a_2$, the operators $U_1$, $U_2$ are obtained explicitly\nin terms of hypergeometric functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 01:35:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-09"}
