ations on the ACF predictions. We find that the observational uncertainty\nin the galaxy luminosity reduces the clustering amplitude and that this effect\nincreases towards faint galaxies, particularly on small scales. To compare\nproperties of model with observed LBGs this uncertainty must be considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 04:40:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2016 05:11:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-15"}
