 and should be relevant for the\nbispectrum of weak gravitational lensing and wider applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 10:22:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2017 14:48:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-20"}
