ecurity using formal methods, its performance via real-world\nbenchmarks, and its usability through a cognitive walkthrough.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 15:37:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 15:35:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2016 12:18:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-30"}
