el explains in particular the RKKY nature of the exchange in\n(Zn,Mn)Te/(Cd,Mn)Te and the double exchange type in (Ga,Mn)N and simultaneously\nthe reason why (Ga,Mn)As exhibits the highest critical temperature among both\nII-VI and III-V DMS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 15:54:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-09"}
